..TEXT:
|Casa~: the Amidei. -- |Fleto~ (Latin ^fletus~),
`weeping.' -- The bloody feud between the Amidei and the
Buondelmonti divided all Florence for a long time.  Cf. G.
Villani, ^Croniche~, V, xxxviii.
